📊 Unit Economics
Core Formula
LTV = ARPU × Lifetime  
CAC = Customer Acquisition Cost  
Unit Economics = LTV / CAC
📈 Individual Expert (Example)
ARPU: €20 / month
Lifetime: 12 months
LTV: €240
CAC: €20–50

→ LTV/CAC = 4–10 (healthy model)

📈 Team Product
ARPU: €500 / month
Lifetime: 18 months
LTV: €9,000
CAC: €500–1,500

→ LTV/CAC = 6+

📈 Enterprise
ARPU: €50k / year
Lifetime: 3 years
LTV: €150k
CAC: €5k–20k

→ LTV/CAC = 7–20

